video.title: Zig & Sharko
video.synopsis: Hungry hyena Zig keeps trying to eat Marina the mermaid for lunch, but her devoted pal Sharko always comes to the rescue in time.

episodes.synopsis: Zig is overjoyed to see Marina on the beach. / Zig uses his sudden popularity to look like a hero. / Marina tries to re-educate the loony pilot.
episodes.title: What a Day! / Beach Hero / Back to Civilization

episodes.synopsis: Sharko feels pressure to impress Poseidon. / Zig struggles to be a baby dolphin's favorite playmate. / Zig and Bernie get a taste of the good life.
episodes.title: Father-in-Law  / Stuffed Animals / Castle Life

episodes.synopsis: Zig and Bernie pretend the cargo plane can fly. / Bernie tries to pull a fast one on Zig. / Zig appears, distraught over the loony pilot's health.
episodes.title: Zig Airlines / Mermaid Fritter  / A Mysterious Guest

episodes.synopsis: Panic ensues when a meteorite is seen heading toward Earth. / A dance club opens at the beach. / Marina becomes obsessed with surfing.
episodes.title: End of the World /  Let’s Dance! / Sea, Surf and Fun

episodes.synopsis: Zig dons a fake moustache on the beach. / A crafty fisherman comes looking for Zig. / Sharko's plan to ditch his new shoes hits a snag.
episodes.title: Bad Hair Day / Fishing for Hyenas / Run, Sharko, Run!

episodes.synopsis: A visiting conquistador has eyes for Marina. / Sharko, Zig and Bernie take on the orcas in rugby. / Zig and Bernie offer to clean the castle.
episodes.title: The Conquistador / Game Over ... Not!  / Spick and Span

episodes.synopsis: Sharko takes his new job a little too seriously. / Bernie gives Zig a bionic upgrade. / Zig and Sharko open a snack bar on the beach.
episodes.title: A Whistle for Sharko / Bionic Zig / Zig and Sharko on the Rocks

episodes.synopsis: Nobody cares for Marina's new suitor. / Zig and Bernie install mermaid traps in the castle. / Zig learns his magic skills are no match for Sharko's.
episodes.title: The Master of the Volcano / Let’s Get Fit / It's Magic!

episodes.synopsis: Sharko tries to keep Marina from eating candy. / Zig's mermaid bait works a bit too well. / A mysterious ink sprayer worries everyone on the beach.
episodes.title: A Sweet Tooth / The Scent of the Hyena / Bodyguard

episodes.synopsis: Sharko gives self-defense lessons on the beach. / Zig sees that Marina isn't scared of him -- at all. / Marina loses her favorite starfish accessory.
episodes.title: Self-Defense Academy / A Generous Mermaid / Catch a Falling Star

episodes.synopsis: Sharko's plans for romance are interrupted. / Zig's not the only one with eyes on the mermaid. / Zig gets some new fans in the form of giant lizards.
episodes.title: Lousy Beach Drivers / A Relative Problem / King of the Animal World

episodes.synopsis: The secret to an old friendship is revealed. / A skateboard brings back memories for Zig. / It used to be three's company for Zig, Sharko and Bernie.
episodes.title: Bosom Buddies / Teen Rebels/ Playtime

episodes.synopsis: Marina finds a tourist-friendly disguise for Sharko. / Zig and Sharko compete for Marina's attention. / Bernie doesn't cast Sharko in his film.
episodes.title: Tourists  / Teacher’s Pet  / Rolling, Action!

episodes.synopsis: Marina's relaxation is ruined by a fly. / Zig steals a unicorn's horn, much to Sharko's dismay. / Zig finds a shrinking raygun in the wrecked plane.
episodes.title: Buzzing Around / Unicorn Blues / Tinky Toys

episodes.synopsis: Bernie goes toe-to-toe with an alien. / Marina asks for help taking care of an unhatched egg. / Zig and Sharko work together to escape the jungle.
episodes.title: The Invader / Daddy Dearest / Lost in the Jungle

episodes.synopsis: Zig pretends to be a dog to get close to Marina. / Zig goes undercover as a cocoon. / Zig offers Marina some ill-advised beauty advice.
episodes.title: Daddy's Little Doggy / Marina Goes Farming / Hair-Do, Hair-Don’t !

episodes.synopsis: Marina sets out to climb a mountain but Sharko isn't far behind. / Marina meets a friendly mummy in a pyramid. / Bernie plus bubble gum equals trouble.
episodes.title: High on the Mountaintop /  The Mummy / Bubble-Gum

episodes.synopsis: Sharko's romantic plans are thwarted by a movie poster. / Sharko tries to hypnotize Zig into becoming a vegetarian. / A mummy puts a curse on Zig.
episodes.title: Movie Night / Veggiezig / The Curse

episodes.synopsis: Zig, Sharko and Marina deal with a sudden bit of sinking. / Sharko's new find impresses Marina. / Zig and Bernie plan to steal Marina's necklace.
episodes.title: That Sinking Feeling /The Moo Can / The Heist

episodes.synopsis: Hades disguises himself as a panda to impress Marina. / A photo of Zig goes viral. / Marina sets out to break the record for tightrope walking.
episodes.title: An Evil Panda / LOL Zig / High-Wired

episodes.synopsis: Marina "borrows" her dad's magic trident. / Zig and Bernie find immediate use for their new trampolines. / Marina is smitten with her model train.
episodes.title: A Three-Pronged Disaster / Boing! Boing! / Little Train, Big Adventure

episodes.synopsis: Sharko has his hands full after a game of Red Light, Green Light. / Zig's cannonball stunt doesn't go as planned. / Zig teaches Sharko how to cook.
episodes.title: Red Light, Green Light  /  The Fall  /  Zig Top Chef

episodes.synopsis: Marina competes in a beauty contest. / Sharko vows to rewind time to save Marina. / Zig and Bernie scare Sharko by pretending to be vampires.
episodes.title: Miss Beach / Catch You on the Rewind / Dance of the Vampire

episodes.synopsis: New ponies test Zig and Bernie's talents in the saddle. / Magnets keep Zig and Sharko together. / Teleportation portals could help Zig nab Marina.
episodes.title: Front Runner / The Power of Attraction / Choice Morsels

episodes.synopsis: Sharko tests his DIY skills on the castle. / Zig challenges Sharko to a not-so-friendly game of tennis. / A busted boiler causes havoc on the island.
episodes.title: DIY Sharko & Invisible Zig / Game, Set and Match /  Heat Wave

episodes.synopsis: Zig tries to botch Sharko's declaration of love. / Zig stumbles across a most intriguing little box. / Zig uses cheese to make Sharko's breath stinky.
episodes.title: The Proposal /  Disco in the Dark /  The Toothpaste
